A na-asụ Santrokofi ma ọ bụ Selee (Sεl__wol____wol____wol__, aha ndị mmadụ na asụsụ) n'akụkụ ugwu nke etiti mpaghara Volta nke Ghana
Ọ bụ otu n'ime asụsụ ugwu Ghana Togo (nke a na-akpọkarị Togorestsprachen ma ọ bụ asụsụ Togo Remnant) nke alaka Kwa nke Niger China.
